{"tid":1534581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有人同我入嚟推爆佢推到上熱門","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:34:16.000Z","uid":199720,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cb890df020fd4d373833fcdede6136a2db77ccd7","tid":1534581,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到依家文宣po少得可憐</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有人同我推到上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHOUU15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHOUU15.png&h=9692df24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#民主及人權法案集會<br />\n9月8日（星期日）下午2時<br />\n美國註港澳領事館(中環花園道26號)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROsbcOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROsbcOQ.png&h=8da00b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1QyJOop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1QyJOop.jpg&h=7a448628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51c7c7ebd29e829c392eab874ee41c1e02c1cdc6","tid":1534581,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22d1108a7eea3fa5fe3fa4f618b121afa4021fee","tid":1534581,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"102b25158572e6c1a376c2f4e8dbd4588ae99f08","tid":1534581,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d742fc6c06aeb8d2d598fdbfc2dfe2697678fa8a","tid":1534581,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2612484632c853c056e30cbbfab93d18551348","tid":1534581,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f6794c0e3782872867a0e6b74e328fd7f79c113b","tid":1534581,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"下完全唔知7號有！！！"},{"pid":"202eeac693fafa952bbbb22ca21f02fa11abee6d","tid":1534581,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03